videos.headline: Melrose credits Penguins' character to make Final
videos.description: Barry Melrose explains why it is so hard for a team to repeat as Stanley Cup champions and notes how much fresher Nashville will be compared to Pittsburgh when the teams meet.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Analysis (Melrose credits Penguins' character to make Final) 2017/05/25 SC

videos.headline: Crosby: 'Great opportunity to play for Stanley Cup'
videos.description: Sidney Crosby shares his thoughts with Linda Cohn on how the Penguins were able to defeat the Senators in Game 7 of the Eastern Conference finals and explains how excited he is to play for the Stanley Cup.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Crosby: 'Great opportunity to play for Stanley Cup') 2017/05/25 SC

videos.headline: Kunitz speechless after game winner
videos.description: Chris Kunitz explains to Linda Cohn what it feels like to score the game-winning goal in Game 7 against the Senators that lifted the Penguins to the Stanley Cup Final.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Kunitz speechless after game winner) 2017/05/25
